{"type": "article", "id": 25052, "title": "这家看上去很冷淡的小店，是一个卖披萨卷的地方", "description": "在这样的地方吃，不知道心里会不会感到奇妙的反差。", "date": "2016-04-07T07:28:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3000, "name": "店铺设计"}, {"id": 9, "name": "意大利"}, {"id": 6289, "name": "小吃"}, {"id": 25903, "name": "coppu"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 181, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021630391GfAjLsnZ3Rvmbzt.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>Pizza 这样的食品在西方也许是最主流的食物之一。一般卖炸鸡的街头小店或以油炸食品为主的快餐店，店铺很多是热闹的红色，带给人一种温暖和快乐的气氛。</p>\n<p>但这家开在在意大利法维尼亚纳岛(Favignana)的街头小吃店 U’coppu 却是极简干净的北欧风，他们出售这种装在纸杯里的 Pizza，握在手里像是握着一个甜筒冰激凌，走在街上很有回头率。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163031iO8eDqToVSfRp6aG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">pizza cup</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163031ut9oTpR5bvOejXKA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24869792\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">pizza cup</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">店铺开在了一个老房子里，进门后就能看到对应的拱形结构。墙面是白色的，用黑色金属勾画了它的圆拱形轮廓，很有线条感。从圆拱轮廓的中间延伸出来一排架子将房间分为两个部分，一半是就餐区，另一半是分配食物的柜台。</p>\n<p class=\"\">店铺使用了几种基本的材料，浅色的雪松木铺在了地板和部分墙面上，黑色的金属框架作为线条强调了结构，最后点缀上玻璃罩和玻璃灯，搭配纯白色的墙面让整体空间简练干净。在这样的地方吃油炸食品，也许能感受到家庭的温馨吧。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163032a6cr1JRNOSG8CoTV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163032i5gDrUsenK0W8hGT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070216303306RFxrGXDiEaV3BL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">可以清晰看到纹路的雪松木。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163033uXv7NItKrZSaxkCl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">正对着柜台还能看到街头小吃的影子，尤其是金属框和一串裸露的灯泡，但也已经变得整齐而有艺术感。柜台上的玻璃罩子有一排圆形的漏孔，可以插入卷起来的小吃。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163034CgaSy18rTpZ92QdW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021630340YNHwzOQr2oayZMi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021630350I5Mr7B3Q9ZdWAoj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163035t4TrgchkBx0U6Qpy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163036zNOq0dILB4StjomX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">柜台和就餐区只是店铺三分之一的面积，剩下的部分还有厨房和实验室。圆拱门的中间是玻璃窗，让人直观看到里面厨房的样子。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163036pQA09nH5SvC7GFIe.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163037ChlqxjB1UsuZSvkH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49112426\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163037ODZobl9UkzAg8L6f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.801854\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021630381tKkDqRIMsTfpeXF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76905312\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/784701/u-coppu-studio-didea\">archdaily</a></p>\n\n"}